The README.md has instructions on how to run it but it's a little out of date in setting up the server  side but I assume anyone actively here knows how to do that. The goal here was to follow the sdk spec and hide any of the proto code from the user.   

I never did anymore clean up since there was no intent on using it. Feel free to cherry pick
